name: Page Life
description:
A cute game where you, the mother birb, protect your young egg carrying it back to your nest. Learn about the life of an artist on the way.

Game made as a final project for UCSC AGPM/CMPM class 120.

Head Artist - Pace Mendoza

Head Programmer - Alenis Lennelluc

Head Designer, Assistant coder and artist, particle effects artist - William Porter
